  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "3e344847",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Content-Based Models for Vietnamese News\n",
    "\n",
    "## Available Models:\n",
    "1. **PhoBERT** (`vinai/phobert-base`) - BERT pretrained trên tiếng Việt\n",
    "2. **SimCSE Vietnamese** (`VoVanPhuc/sup-SimCSE-VietNamese-phobert-base`) - Tối ưu cho sentence similarity  \n",
    "3. **Hybrid** - Kết hợp Collaborative Filtering + Content-based\n",
    "\n",
    "## Cách hoạt động:\n",
    "- Encode nội dung bài viết (title + description) bằng PhoBERT\n",
    "- Tính user preference từ trung bình các bài đã đọc\n",
    "- Recommend bài tương tự với preference của user"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "f4d96aeb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "\u001b[33mWARNING: Running pip as the 'root' user can result in broken permissions and conflicting behaviour with the system package manager, possibly rendering your system unusable. It is recommended to use a virtual environment instead: https://pip.pypa.io/warnings/venv. Use the --root-user-action option if you know what you are doing and want to suppress this warning.\u001b[0m\u001b[33m\n",
      "\u001b[0m"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# 4. Install dependencies for PhoBERT (if needed)\n",
    "!pip install transformers sentencepiece underthesea -q"
